            I'm a Frontend Engineer with 7+ years of experience designing and building high-performance web applications. My main focus is React, Next.js, and modern frontend architecture — always striving for scalable solutions, clean UI/UX, accessibility, and best development practices.
          </p>
          <p>
            I collaborate closely with clients to turn ideas into polished digital products, whether that's a custom WordPress site or a fully responsive and interactive web platform.
          </p>
          <p>
            As I continue to grow, I'm expanding my skills into backend development and cloud-driven architectures — aiming to deliver complete, end-to-end solutions with strong engineering foundations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bts">
